r skills and equipment to find a combat style that’s perfect for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419160/extras/4f5332f84282e93dba4216368f307498.webp?t=1720187905\" width=24 height=24 /></span> An interconnected world: Discover a sprawling handcrafted landscape filled with treasures, tough-as-nails bosses and secret pathways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419160/extras/4f5332f84282e93dba4216368f307498.webp?t=1720187905\" width=24 height=24 /></span> 16-bit sensation: Terragaya comes to life with vibrant world-class pixel art packed to the brim with details.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419160/extras/4f5332f84282e93dba4216368f307498.webp?t=1720187905\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Smart moves: Solve environmental puzzles and leap from place to place using an ever-expanding moveset.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419160/extras/9c5dcfb07f82620357074b894c6b3183.poster.avif?t=1720187905\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419160/extras/9c5dcfb07f82620357074b894c6b3183.webm?t=1720187905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1419160/extras/9c5dcfb07f82620357074b894c6b3183.mp4?t=1720187905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
